/>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"但高度文明都未必控制到所有野。<br />\n<br />\n可能有日佢地星球發生重大事，要翻地球人幫手"},{"pid":"c8c879f127965197b81b51a781ccf6e3d513e11b","tid":731609,"uid":7311,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"e6cd22686a97d8a7eb0d8485e2b7cfff3960dd21","tid":731609,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"連登討論區單機中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"討論之前你真係信佢所講事件/研究真確性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e5e695450e630f3a4989cc914ab98e84f62f0c","tid":731609,"uid":60100,"like":161,"dislike":2,"score":159,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"其實依加都有厭氧生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6138ff072a23d7136ceff8137048717e81ac434","tid":731609,"uid":177089,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"依家環境入面都有厭氧生物 點解唔係因為帶氧型生命進化比厭氧型更加快所以令後者滅絕？ <br />\n<br />\n除咗氧氣呢個溫室環境 仲有輻射 重力 真空都係令人脫離唔到地球 點解要針對氧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c198abcf6c04ae4d0181d47cd3cafe056a20b6","tid":731609,"uid":188,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"你出呢個po<br />\n我呢個回覆 都係外星人控制緊"},{"pid":"808e2e2e1dfcc6d319315eb703550e56ede4f35b","tid":731609,"uid":33213,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"0789cf624d19c32afe9fcb1f16247375f2fee721","tid":731609,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c8c879f127965197b81b51a781ccf6e3d513e11b","tid":731609,"uid":7311,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"e6cd22686a97d8a7eb0d8485e2b7cfff3960dd21","tid":731609,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06