:"4a96296a4a5608b4d4b766b10060b6217bd6b0fb","tid":731609,"uid":86125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98ad66b5fb614d2037492ed0ed5f924646aecd86","tid":731609,"uid":147721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"57e0c4e813235037920eb65dbab76fa518552ea0","tid":731609,"uid":172754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f901f37a538a4a28d7a4af40c5fe441d49f6289","tid":731609,"uid":147721,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知唔知有氧代謝既轉換效率高無氧代謝幾多倍</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"唔知wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 真心想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:07:00.000Z","msg":"一般被廣泛接納既估算 係<br />\nyield of fermentation = 2 ATP/ glucose<br />\nyield of aerobic respiration = 32 ATP/glucose<br />\n(source: <a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Sebastian_Bonhoeffer/publication/12050915_Cooperation_and_Competition_in_the_Evolution_of_ATP-Producing_Pathways/links/0912f510a8c6a033d2000000.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FSebastian_Bonhoeffer%2Fpublication%2F12050915_Cooperation_and_Competition_in_the_Evolution_of_ATP-Producing_Pathways%2Flinks%2F0912f510a8c6a033d2000000.pdf&d=0eyK77BLoCEK96fm%2BgHxWKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=7ece90d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Sebastian_Bonhoeffer/publication/12050915_Cooperation_and_Competition_in_the_Evolution_of_ATP-Producing_Pathways/links/0912f510a8c6a033d2000000.pdf</a>)<br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲數字就只係估算黎 因為實際上有太多步驟參與 未必真係有咁多yield<br />\n例如呢篇咁(<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/8988933_The_molecular_machinery_of_Keilin's_respiratory_chain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F8988933_The_molecular_machinery_of_Keilin%27s_respiratory_chain&d=0eyK77BLoCEK96fm%2BgHxWKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=42d4b1e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/publication/8988933_The_molecular_machinery_of_Keilin's_respiratory_chain</a>) 就估算yield of aerobic respiration = 29.85 ATP/glucose<br />\n<br />\n至於其他既ATP合成途徑 例如sulfate reduction/metal reduction 就搵唔到paper講yield 靠其他巴打提供資料了"},{"pid":"2932ba197b50fb8b8b3742b553caf29c5e667b23","tid":731609,"uid":174493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"外星人既野除左羅馬教廷就係共濟會有記錄，一個1717年已經存在既組織點都會有記載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}